## 5. The Git Workflow

### Standard Daily Cycle

```
1. git pull          ← Get latest changes from teammates
2. Edit your files   ← Do the work
3. git status        ← See what changed
4. git add .         ← Stage the changes
5. git commit -m ""  ← Save a permanent snapshot
6. git push          ← Upload your commits to the remote
```

